  <div class="container">
    <h1>About</h1>

    <p>
      I'm Jonathan Malkin. I build tools for communities that mainstream tech ignores.
    </p>

    <p>
      I left a 20+ year career in enterprise technology in June 2025. Presales, solutions engineering, business analysis, project management. Jobs that combined technical expertise with communication skills to translate between different audiences. Good jobs, but not the work I wanted to do for the rest of my life.
    </p>

    <p>
      Now I'm a solo founder building software, assessment tools, and educational content for underserved communities.
    </p>

    <h2>What I Build</h2>

    <ul>
      <li><strong><a href="https://quiz.9archetypes.app">Kink Archetypes</a></strong> &mdash;
        Personality assessment for adult audiences exploring kink education. 200+ daily users.
        The thesis: kink education is on the same taboo-to-mainstream trajectory that meditation
        and mental health took over the past decade.</li>
      <li><strong><a href="/jules/">Jules</a></strong> &mdash; Open-source AI assistant framework
        built on Claude Code. 33 skills, 15 rules, 12 hooks. The infrastructure that powers
        the business.</li>
      <li><strong><a href="/articles/">Articles &amp; Newsletter</a></strong> &mdash; Writing about
        Claude Code, AI agents, and building as a solo founder.</li>
      <li><strong>Technical advisory</strong> &mdash; Available for AI infrastructure and
        automation consulting.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      Next up: more tools in the kink education space (interest exploration, negotiation frameworks)
      plus personal development assessments for general audiences.
    </p>

    <h2>Four Pillars</h2>

    <p>
      I organize my life and work around four pillars:
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li><strong>Purpose:</strong> Do work that visibly and directly impacts real people.</li>
      <li><strong>People:</strong> Be around people I enjoy, personally and professionally.</li>
      <li><strong>Profit:</strong> Build a profitable, independent business on my own terms.</li>
      <li><strong>Health:</strong> Maintain and deepen physical, mental, and emotional health.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      Everything I write and build traces back to these. Purpose is the north star. The others are the foundation it stands on.
    </p>

    <h2>Background</h2>

    <p>
      Based in Austin, Texas. Systems thinker. Teacher at heart. Deeply values liberty, consent, and individual responsibility. Thinks by talking. Builds by doing.
    </p>

